vanamala is a 1951 indian malayalam film , directed by g viswanath and produced by v&c productions .   the film stars p. a. thomas , ammini in lead roles .   the film had musical score by ps divakar .   it is the first jungle movie in malayalam .   also the debut film of neyyattinkara komalam , director g .   viswanath , lyricist p. kunjukrishna menon , singer jikki and cameraman arumugham .